H0.text: In the King James Version, which eponymous book of the Old Testament follows 'Esther' and precedes 'Psalms'. Ecclesiastes

H1.text: In the King James Version, which eponymous book of the Old Testament follows 'Esther' and precedes 'Psalms'. Song of Solomon

H2.text: In the King James Version, which eponymous book of the Old Testament follows 'Esther' and precedes 'Psalms'. Ruth

H3.text: In the King James Version, which eponymous book of the Old Testament follows 'Esther' and precedes 'Psalms'. Job

A4.text: In the Latin Vulgate, the New Revised Standard Version, and in Protestant Bibles, it is placed after the Book of Esther as the first of the poetic books.
